[
  {
    "text": "We are joined this morning by one of the biggest names in business tech and philanthropy. Bill Gates",
    "uid": "d7250328bd311996",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 0.34,
    "end": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": "co-founded Microsoft nearly 50 years ago.",
    "uid": "54a491815321c398",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 5.56,
    "end": 8.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Since 2000 he has supported causes around the globe by giving away nearly 60 billion dollars",
    "uid": "ee24c23fc78b4e68",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 8.94,
    "end": 14.7
  },
  {
    "text": "through his Gates Foundation.",
    "uid": "9c905613014df7b1",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 14.7,
    "end": 16.18
  },
  {
    "text": "His newest project is a Netflix series is called What's Next, The Future with Bill Gates.",
    "uid": "4309112fe732d498",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 16.18,
    "end": 21.98
  },
  {
    "text": "And in it, he examines ways to solve some of the biggest challenges we face to date, including",
    "uid": "a8dfff29850daab9",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 21.98,
    "end": 27.26
  },
  {
    "text": "the use of AI.",
    "uid": "6a441d38572eeba0",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 27.26,
    "end": 28.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Climate change, creating responsible AI.",
    "uid": "2f951f08a5424670",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 28.74,
    "end": 33.42
  },
  {
    "text": "In this information.",
    "uid": "46d9e0f180b2def0",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 33.42,
    "end": 34.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Income in a wallet.",
    "uid": "a87faa1fdc662e74",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 34.42,
    "end": 35.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Dealing with infectious diseases.",
    "uid": "3e042996c147f10f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 35.7,
    "end": 37.74
  },
  {
    "text": "But I believe we can solve them.",
    "uid": "f684855821bf2b62",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 37.74,
    "end": 41.34
  },
  {
    "text": "How will artificial intelligence impact society?",
    "uid": "3e4f0c45060a1515",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 41.34,
    "end": 44.9
  },
  {
    "text": "Crafted text to my son using Gen Z slang.",
    "uid": "8704b5553c1e0ffc",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 44.9,
    "end": 48.42
  },
  {
    "text": "Your fam, what's good, how you vibe in.",
    "uid": "e15d738233a78e28",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 48.42,
    "end": 52.18
  },
  {
    "text": "How you vibe in.",
    "uid": "768be13b0cc2f18b",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 52.18,
    "end": 53.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Good to have you.",
    "uid": "ca01321f341917a3",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 54.46,
    "end": 55.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for being here.",
    "uid": "4a0ecf7a62d2afe0",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 55.46,
    "end": 56.46
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks for asking me.",
    "uid": "ff157dfc69de98f0",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 56.46,
    "end": 57.46
  },
  {
    "text": "I was talking before we came on about the series we've all watched it.",
    "uid": "3a689d651f3e783e",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 58.46,
    "end": 61.58
  },
  {
    "text": "It really is fascinating and you take a unique approach.",
    "uid": "c6981341095e55a0",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 61.58,
    "end": 64.78
  },
  {
    "text": "What you malaria, eradicating malaria, misinformation, climate change and you talk about ways",
    "uid": "31fb8b20c8526688",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 64.78,
    "end": 70.42
  },
  {
    "text": "perhaps we can solve some of earth's most daunting problems.",
    "uid": "a6a0caaabba48291",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 70.42,
    "end": 74.06
  },
  {
    "text": "How did you come up with the topics and what was the images for the series?",
    "uid": "a64e8ec5375d940f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 74.06,
    "end": 78.54
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, I'm very lucky I get to work on AI.",
    "uid": "1ab6655219e1311e",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 78.54,
    "end": 81.82
  },
  {
    "text": "I get to work on global health.",
    "uid": "72ef69b8709b9b2b",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 81.82,
    "end": 85.78
  },
  {
    "text": "These information, so one where I've been a subject of misinformation.",
    "uid": "c66211fc53004536",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 85.78,
    "end": 91.66
  },
  {
    "text": "I talked with Lady Gaga who's had it, even worse.",
    "uid": "a2fa8f4d187abac8",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 91.66,
    "end": 96.58
  },
  {
    "text": "These are things wrong.",
    "uid": "f5b767faa65b1ed2",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 96.58,
    "end": 97.58
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm lucky enough to get to talk to experts.",
    "uid": "03c6ad35e9dd038e",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 97.58,
    "end": 100.34
  },
  {
    "text": "I get asked about them a lot.",
    "uid": "65424c332e08580d",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 100.34,
    "end": 102.18
  },
  {
    "text": "In the opportunity to work with Morgan Nellville and do a series came along and I said, yeah, this",
    "uid": "4ccd675f32892767",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 102.18,
    "end": 107.98
  },
  {
    "text": "will be fun.",
    "uid": "2848cae5cba7daed",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 107.98,
    "end": 108.98
  },
  {
    "text": "The first episode, it grabs my attention because you look at AI and you talk with director James",
    "uid": "6775643af950555d",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 108.98,
    "end": 114.14
  },
  {
    "text": "He was genius because from the creative side we're talking about, oh my goodness, avatar and",
    "uid": "7777761d6237f3c7",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 115.14,
    "end": 119.78
  },
  {
    "text": "He talked about making sure we don't miss some of the warning signs from all of this and he equated",
    "uid": "03243030bd4aea1f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 120.98,
    "end": 125.86
  },
  {
    "text": "it to heading full speed towards the iceberg and people not listening to the warnings.",
    "uid": "82203896260d0331",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 125.86,
    "end": 130.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Talk to me a little bit about, and I also thought it was interesting.",
    "uid": "1d08aebcfc4d30d0",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 130.86,
    "end": 133.58
  },
  {
    "text": "He talked about losing jobs or maybe creativity.",
    "uid": "ca6d88e59edf8230",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 133.58,
    "end": 136.46
  },
  {
    "text": "You brought up losing purpose.",
    "uid": "939fcc2b68917cd3",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 136.46,
    "end": 138.18
  },
  {
    "text": "If computers do everything for you, what am I here for?",
    "uid": "68a89c9d1291f985",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 138.18,
    "end": 141.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Can you talk a little bit about that and what you think of all of it?",
    "uid": "a0955d0d50c9629c",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 141.82,
    "end": 145.1
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, in the near term, the idea of using the AI to help with education, and I've been",
    "uid": "0fd90faa0239e39e",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 145.1,
    "end": 151.38
  },
  {
    "text": "out in the jersey and seen the pilots up in Newark, using it in healthcare and even today,",
    "uid": "2719465c5890f60b",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 151.38,
    "end": 157.62
  },
  {
    "text": "if you get a MRI, you know, putting it in the AI, it'll simplify it for your complex medical",
    "uid": "463dfb92f1ac8fc1",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 157.62,
    "end": 165.3
  },
  {
    "text": "It's so powerful.",
    "uid": "d7c734e0347fe02c",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 166.62,
    "end": 167.62
  },
  {
    "text": "It's the first technology that is happening very quickly and there's no limit.",
    "uid": "cdcc4fc0ca819695",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 167.62,
    "end": 174.06
  },
  {
    "text": "When we had like tractors, it was okay farmers can do other things.",
    "uid": "bbfcf65582e6e7bd",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 174.06,
    "end": 178.7
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, we're talking about almost every kind of job, which should mean more leisure time.",
    "uid": "8766687e987e0258",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 178.7,
    "end": 186.1
  },
  {
    "text": "But then it's going to create a, almost a, wow, what do we do with all that time type problem?",
    "uid": "c32a12cbcd08ef9a",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 186.1,
    "end": 191.94
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, you could definitely see the benefits of AI, but I think all of us kind of have a",
    "uid": "9d9a1843b7313937",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 191.94,
    "end": 196.86
  },
  {
    "text": "fear of it as well.",
    "uid": "acf6b39b569fd82d",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 196.86,
    "end": 198.86
  },
  {
    "text": "It was interesting because some of the experts in the episode said, we don't even know",
    "uid": "5e06031dfefcf147",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 198.86,
    "end": 203.74
  },
  {
    "text": "how it figures out what it does sometimes, which is kind of scary.",
    "uid": "57c274552d27e78a",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 203.74,
    "end": 206.98
  },
  {
    "text": "So do you think companies that are creating these technologies are doing enough to safeguard it",
    "uid": "ff26df698f6d462f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 206.98,
    "end": 212.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, there's certainly a lot of discussion about how should it be regulated.",
    "uid": "2e13d46ff78c44cf",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 213.34,
    "end": 216.94
  },
  {
    "text": "And the companies are saying, yes, the government needs to understand our work and needs to",
    "uid": "7eb7b052e32549c3",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 216.94,
    "end": 221.9
  },
  {
    "text": "look at the right regulations.",
    "uid": "3d5d37c5ecec16fc",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 221.9,
    "end": 224.58
  },
  {
    "text": "At the same time, you know, people saying, okay, the US wants to stay ahead.",
    "uid": "a9ec8e12822e38eb",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 224.58,
    "end": 229.34
  },
  {
    "text": "So whenever we talk about, oh, can we slow it down?",
    "uid": "bbce4d3eefa842e0",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 229.34,
    "end": 231.82
  },
  {
    "text": "They're like, well, don't, don't slow it down.",
    "uid": "fd86e005841ac898",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 231.82,
    "end": 233.7
  },
  {
    "text": "And so it's going to be the most, the biggest change agent in the next 10 years.",
    "uid": "fe2bebe1fd475757",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 234.7,
    "end": 243.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Mostly good stuff, mostly.",
    "uid": "45749a981495f53a",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 243.94,
    "end": 245.94
  },
  {
    "text": "But will we get it right?",
    "uid": "c1511df847602e63",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 245.94,
    "end": 247.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Social media, we're still arguing about, hey, we shouldn't have let young kids use it as much.",
    "uid": "c1041199009bcd8f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 247.94,
    "end": 254.14
  },
  {
    "text": "And how do you balance free speech and versus crazy stuff that got people not to take that",
    "uid": "8bc5abac7f2a1150",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 254.14,
    "end": 261.34
  },
  {
    "text": "seems, for example?",
    "uid": "1f0e57ad2c08699c",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 261.34,
    "end": 262.34
  },
  {
    "text": "And now that the toothpaste is out of the tube, it seems like on social media.",
    "uid": "c2b99acbd37c5af3",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 263.34,
    "end": 265.98
  },
  {
    "text": "I want to just follow up on what you said there.",
    "uid": "7e464fcaa73918b0",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 265.98,
    "end": 268.42
  },
  {
    "text": "How can lawmakers regulate AI or regulate social media for that matter?",
    "uid": "01125ae404a90edf",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 268.42,
    "end": 273.22
  },
  {
    "text": "It seems that most of them don't really understand it.",
    "uid": "b707dfd363fe2d7f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 273.22,
    "end": 275.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, they can create liability, say your AI is giving health advice.",
    "uid": "a6136e54e83fb905",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 275.86,
    "end": 281.54
  },
  {
    "text": "They can say, okay, if you make a mistake there, you're going to be financially responsible.",
    "uid": "438b8656a508f75d",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 281.54,
    "end": 288.1
  },
  {
    "text": "So, if it's discriminatory, you can make them responsible.",
    "uid": "85cfe5027305ad08",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 288.1,
    "end": 296.94
  },
  {
    "text": "Because it's happening so fast, writing the rules is a bit of a challenge.",
    "uid": "707d1a79e44d8669",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 296.94,
    "end": 302.86
  },
  {
    "text": "And so we're trying to encourage the people in government themselves to be users.",
    "uid": "371af85ded89a822",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 302.86,
    "end": 307.82
  },
  {
    "text": "So they understand, wow, this is where it's incredibly good.",
    "uid": "75efc61b61b200e9",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 307.82,
    "end": 312.22
  },
  {
    "text": "This is where it sometimes goes nuts.",
    "uid": "bb6bf01af0581b56",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 312.22,
    "end": 313.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Do you use it?",
    "uid": "3098ab64a68b9934",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 313.86,
    "end": 314.86
  },
  {
    "text": "But I want to summarize a meeting or take a book that I don't have time to read and get",
    "uid": "a0e46258ea0de3b0",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 315.86,
    "end": 322.86
  },
  {
    "text": "the just a bit of it, even to draft some complex set of points, a speech.",
    "uid": "b83e48fa3b5c937a",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 322.86,
    "end": 329.18
  },
  {
    "text": "No, this I highly recommend it.",
    "uid": "04c97b056d8a1338",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 329.18,
    "end": 332.46
  },
  {
    "text": "It saves a lot of time.",
    "uid": "f28a88e926c00d04",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 332.46,
    "end": 333.7
  },
  {
    "text": "It can even write poems and songs in a way that is surprisingly crazy.",
    "uid": "4834b68cab0af129",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 333.7,
    "end": 339.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Have you tried it?",
    "uid": "c1f6e48c980318a1",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 339.3,
    "end": 340.3
  },
  {
    "text": "Have you tried it?",
    "uid": "de3ed0f7cf67a505",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 340.3,
    "end": 341.3
  },
  {
    "text": "I've intimidated by meant to invite.",
    "uid": "0d1436303cc6988c",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 341.3,
    "end": 343.3
  },
  {
    "text": "I have a friend sit down with you.",
    "uid": "48ab8f5fe420f0cb",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 343.3,
    "end": 345.82
  },
  {
    "text": "You need to play around.",
    "uid": "676011c9ee348cbe",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 345.82,
    "end": 346.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Are you being my friend?",
    "uid": "9b3f899f8f64df37",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 346.82,
    "end": 347.82
  },
  {
    "text": "Sorry, I was dead.",
    "uid": "828fcfb9f0c166a4",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 348.82,
    "end": 349.82
  },
  {
    "text": "We got so much we want to talk to you about.",
    "uid": "9bb36400885164bf",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 349.82,
    "end": 351.38
  },
  {
    "text": "We want to pick you up, bring about including something that came up in that Netflix series.",
    "uid": "a0828ab065cc51af",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 351.38,
    "end": 354.86
  },
  {
    "text": "When you sat down with Senator Bernie Sanders, you talked about your own wealth.",
    "uid": "a39aa5fa1194e94c",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 354.86,
    "end": 358.86
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's what he said.",
    "uid": "5db9c2adc07c709c",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 358.86,
    "end": 361.26
  },
  {
    "text": "You are a just a new person.",
    "uid": "3421a130a4dacf90",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 361.26,
    "end": 363.22
  },
  {
    "text": "We are a very innovative guy.",
    "uid": "eea34abd77e37ed3",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 363.22,
    "end": 364.82
  },
  {
    "text": "He deserves financial reward.",
    "uid": "676074a9becafa46",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 364.82,
    "end": 366.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, I do know how much to deserve.",
    "uid": "925d19e9480f602b",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 366.22,
    "end": 368.38
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, we're going to get Bill starts on that.",
    "uid": "8e86fc56f8a09ac1",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 368.38,
    "end": 371.66
  },
  {
    "text": "But after a quick break, much more will be able to get you to third out today.",
    "uid": "a847c5e86f43d1de",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 371.66,
    "end": 374.22
  },
  {
    "text": "Come to my back.",
    "uid": "113cbc8670c13dfe",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 374.22,
    "end": 375.22
  },
  {
    "text": "We're back with tech-tight man philanthropist Bill Gates.",
    "uid": "a5d01fa55ac625fa",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 375.22,
    "end": 382.02
  },
  {
    "text": "His new series What's next?",
    "uid": "9c07810deaf27ee8",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 382.02,
    "end": 383.58
  },
  {
    "text": "The future with Bill Gates is out.",
    "uid": "c24d23f13ff69182",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 383.58,
    "end": 385.62
  },
  {
    "text": "It's on Netflix right now.",
    "uid": "2687308ac6f34885",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 385.62,
    "end": 386.62
  },
  {
    "text": "We encourage everyone to watch.",
    "uid": "6b14c8da9143074d",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 387.62,
    "end": 389.26
  },
  {
    "text": "Before the commercial break there, we played a clip where Senator Bernie Sanders was asking you about",
    "uid": "a080fd920123a079",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 389.26,
    "end": 393.98
  },
  {
    "text": "your personal fortune.",
    "uid": "c1694365e6582116",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 393.98,
    "end": 395.9
  },
  {
    "text": "And it should be noted you have given away billions of dollars of your own wealth to advance",
    "uid": "c38c2ce94be73831",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 395.9,
    "end": 401.42
  },
  {
    "text": "causes and poor countries.",
    "uid": "c4d3b190d4c47920",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 401.42,
    "end": 402.9
  },
  {
    "text": "And promote public health here as well, gender equality.",
    "uid": "86d9f48a28ad7fe4",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 402.9,
    "end": 406.42
  },
  {
    "text": "But does the Senator have a point?",
    "uid": "89cba6d4b8ef6676",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 406.42,
    "end": 407.94
  },
  {
    "text": "I mean, do you think you have enough money and should the government be able to say enough?",
    "uid": "44b828e96e1d9bc5",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 407.94,
    "end": 415.5
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's help redistribute some of that?",
    "uid": "dfc19205180216e1",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 415.5,
    "end": 417.74
  },
  {
    "text": "Yeah, if I just enlarged the tax system, I would have paid a lot more in taxes.",
    "uid": "f41e846d49c88224",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 417.74,
    "end": 422.38
  },
  {
    "text": "I'd have about a third as much money as I have.",
    "uid": "6c3c4ca45f9d8658",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 422.38,
    "end": 425.62
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, Bernie would go further.",
    "uid": "61d346356e975b13",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 425.62,
    "end": 427.14
  },
  {
    "text": "He would basically say that you can never be a billionaire.",
    "uid": "829dadc43cb53308",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 427.14,
    "end": 431.06
  },
  {
    "text": "At that point, the government's going to take way a hundred percent.",
    "uid": "75f4be6fb25e0670",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 431.06,
    "end": 435.34
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'd be worried that the distortions and the disincentive would go to farther.",
    "uid": "5269bee3f572faac",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 435.34,
    "end": 442.34
  },
  {
    "text": "Maybe I'm biased.",
    "uid": "01584a98091f5d0f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 442.34,
    "end": 444.5
  },
  {
    "text": "But I would collect a lot more from people like myself in order to reduce the deficit and",
    "uid": "8f1c8c7fe597a759",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 444.5,
    "end": 452.14
  },
  {
    "text": "have a more generous safety net.",
    "uid": "3afd78812a9f4a34",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 452.14,
    "end": 454.06
  },
  {
    "text": "So you feel like the ultra wealthy should be paying more.",
    "uid": "369bcd649d650bcb",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 454.06,
    "end": 457.38
  },
  {
    "text": "We should pay more.",
    "uid": "08951d38fe4d4e71",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 457.38,
    "end": 458.38
  },
  {
    "text": "How much more?",
    "uid": "06eb1eb53ff1240d",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 458.38,
    "end": 460.38
  },
  {
    "text": "The tax on labor and the tax on capital.",
    "uid": "0c2af3a8187f310a",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 460.94,
    "end": 467.02
  },
  {
    "text": "There's always been this argument that do need to treat capital especially.",
    "uid": "4bfe7ee6ee0ef0eb",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 467.02,
    "end": 470.98
  },
  {
    "text": "And I don't go along with that.",
    "uid": "c333aae1bd150a5e",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 470.98,
    "end": 473.34
  },
  {
    "text": "I think capital gains and ordinary income we should tax at the same rate.",
    "uid": "a879a9bb1f6ec9cf",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 473.34,
    "end": 478.3
  },
  {
    "text": "So, and I'm also a big believer in the state tax.",
    "uid": "19de145eea888c57",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 478.3,
    "end": 482.14
  },
  {
    "text": "Actually, my dad is deceased and I did a lot of work saying, hey, this is how you prevent",
    "uid": "dbdb8cdaf79cb68d",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 482.14,
    "end": 488.38
  },
  {
    "text": "the kindness these and encourage people to do more philanthropy.",
    "uid": "42f22f73132617eb",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 488.38,
    "end": 493.38
  },
  {
    "text": "You have to slide the higher taxes, but you let people do philanthropy.",
    "uid": "4a29104e96f48376",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 493.38,
    "end": 498.38
  },
  {
    "text": "That's really great.",
    "uid": "a0f67118b339af36",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 498.38,
    "end": 500.38
  },
  {
    "text": "We really appreciate your perspective.",
    "uid": "7fa4c400d5f63411",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 500.38,
    "end": 501.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Very rarely do we have guests with all three different things.",
    "uid": "034f9c3ca2422c86",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 501.38,
    "end": 504.38
  },
  {
    "text": "I also want to bring up the fact that the show also highlights the progress in fighting disease.",
    "uid": "405d77bd288b4dac",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 504.38,
    "end": 509.38
  },
  {
    "text": "That's certainly what grabbed my attention.",
    "uid": "d49ca7ff5358a7f4",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 509.38,
    "end": 511.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Obviously, you've done so much work in the fighting against malaria.",
    "uid": "3f323a48ddc7afed",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 511.38,
    "end": 514.38
  },
  {
    "text": "It's been a long time caused for you.",
    "uid": "badadd6160109793",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 514.38,
    "end": 516.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Speaking of health, I remember during COVID, you talked about how we have to be careful and you worried about what happened.",
    "uid": "d028b0a3899cf65d",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 516.38,
    "end": 522.38
  },
  {
    "text": "If we were to have another pandemic, does that still rent space in your mind or what do you think?",
    "uid": "dfa07cc64a665c70",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 522.38,
    "end": 526.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Yes, sadly, when the pandemic ended, I thought, okay, now we're going to sit around and talk about what people will be well and how we'll do better next time.",
    "uid": "a7a5ef213d94ca29",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 526.38,
    "end": 534.38
  },
  {
    "text": "But people are like, no, don't bring that up.",
    "uid": "602c1ad556e376a6",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 534.38,
    "end": 537.38
  },
  {
    "text": "It's so divisive in terms of, you know, partisan views about what went well and what didn't.",
    "uid": "86a0612692ad68c6",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 537.38,
    "end": 544.38
  },
  {
    "text": "That we're not preparing ourselves for the next one.",
    "uid": "73144486b6ce1738",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 544.38,
    "end": 547.38
  },
  {
    "text": "And I'm hopeful, you know, as things calm down a little bit, people will go back and say, wait a minute, if we don't have good health systems in Africa, they can't catch these things early and stop them from glowing global.",
    "uid": "d32b220327d375f2",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 547.38,
    "end": 559.38
  },
  {
    "text": "And, of course, the cost was so gigantic that making sure you see it early and stop it is worth all along.",
    "uid": "35fb787cac31218a",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 559.38,
    "end": 566.38
  },
  {
    "text": "I think we can't prevent what you can.",
    "uid": "8289c53a6e473786",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 566.38,
    "end": 568.38
  },
  {
    "text": "One of your episodes tackles climate change.",
    "uid": "92b6f56a4453a2df",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 568.38,
    "end": 570.38
  },
  {
    "text": "You became a grandparent last year.",
    "uid": "ee9a8e32a8d16c05",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 570.38,
    "end": 572.38
  },
  {
    "text": "We all have several kids between all of us.",
    "uid": "c79b010632cd3d3e",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 572.38,
    "end": 576.38
  },
  {
    "text": "What kind of world do you think we are leaving for our kids?",
    "uid": "1c569da72d7ac854",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 576.38,
    "end": 580.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Did that kind of increase your sense of urgency to sort of fix some of the things?",
    "uid": "7aefc058955f7a1f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 580.38,
    "end": 584.38
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, my first grandchild is actually here in New York City and couldn't be cuter.",
    "uid": "b14645664e15b795",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 585.38,
    "end": 591.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Just about water.",
    "uid": "170b8f3740565d69",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 591.38,
    "end": 594.38
  },
  {
    "text": "And, you know, wow, that means the world, you know, 50, 60 years ago will be the world that she lives in.",
    "uid": "bb5311b196a99f3b",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 595.38,
    "end": 604.38
  },
  {
    "text": "And we're not making enough progress, you know, and the damage kind of accumulates over time.",
    "uid": "2a90af726c1df6de",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 604.38,
    "end": 610.38
  },
  {
    "text": "So the need to innovate, I met a lot of young activists who are really harsh about, you know, we're not doing enough.",
    "uid": "fd7e261d6464462f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 610.38,
    "end": 619.38
  },
  {
    "text": "I found that inspiring and motivating.",
    "uid": "b2f59bcf0de5bbf4",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 619.38,
    "end": 623.38
  },
  {
    "text": "So there are people working to make change.",
    "uid": "73bab33d739a60bb",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 623.38,
    "end": 625.38
  },
  {
    "text": "There's almost too many causes right now.",
    "uid": "08b5903115cdfd22",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 627.38,
    "end": 629.38
  },
  {
    "text": "You know, you've got wars.",
    "uid": "63c25d64577eb6ef",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 629.38,
    "end": 631.38
  },
  {
    "text": "You've got interest payments.",
    "uid": "9a3a6060a81db393",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 631.38,
    "end": 634.38
  },
  {
    "text": "It's it's it's a time where, you know, making sure we pick the right things and set our priorities will be challenging.",
    "uid": "f4b8cbf570b77083",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 634.38,
    "end": 642.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Bill Gates, we love that you sound hopeful.",
    "uid": "03c9d3d395890323",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 644.38,
    "end": 646.38
  },
  {
    "text": "You can watch what's next.",
    "uid": "32f283d823baffd9",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 654.38,
    "end": 655.38
  },
  {
    "text": "The future with Bill Gates streaming now on Netflix.",
    "uid": "a5d35b72151da9f6",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 655.38,
    "end": 656.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, thanks for watching.",
    "uid": "37a34adfa1f2412f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 656.38,
    "end": 657.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Don't miss the today show every week day at 11 a.m. Eastern 8 Pacific on our streaming channel.",
    "uid": "04c28e83a9438d4f",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
    "start": 657.38,
    "end": 662.38
  },
  {
    "text": "Today all day to watch head to today dot com slash all day or click the link right here.",
    "uid": "54907b66e6f0b4b5",
    "source": "TODAY - Bill_Gates_talks_new_Netflix_series_shares_how_he_uses_AI_in_his_life",
